{"tid":2392712,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【伯明翰】創業容易 中小企落腳","createTime":"2021-02-03T03:30:49.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-03T12:36:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"64b47c34d94834cab6602548cf858d8d20c04cf2","tid":2392712,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:30:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/MJFORX2FBVGVHPETCOXWRLQFW4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2FMJFORX2FBVGVHPETCOXWRLQFW4%2F&d=FM8PVMPbIH5fyb1BVmxPrS3IRifvRw8PV%2BxDOhj55DY%3D&h=9ee20a6c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210203%2FMJFORX2FBVGVHPETCOXWRLQFW4%2F&h=7cc14b19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210203/MJFORX2FBVGVHPETCOXWRLQFW4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n【伯明翰】創業容易 中小企落腳<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hapDmnEFsOEpiNpngjGMzFWnwIY=/1000x563/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/AJ2UQM4EQVD65JISWXRA4FPOKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhapDmnEFsOEpiNpngjGMzFWnwIY%3D%2F1000x563%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FAJ2UQM4EQVD65JISWXRA4FPOKQ.jpg&h=21363688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■已移居伯明翰20年的Tommy，認為這裏發展潛力甚高。<br />\n<br />\n在香港出生的陳書敏（Tommy）前後居英約20年，其中伯明翰住了七年，更設有自己公司。他坦言倫敦最似香港，但伯明翰很有潛力，而且樓價低倫敦逾六成，容易生活及創業。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【卡迪夫】空氣水質佳 物價較低<br />\n<br />\n「The next big thing after London.（繼倫敦後下一個大城）」要Tommy用一句話概括伯明翰，他着眼於其潛力。租金廉宜，就業機會多、大學林立，很多年輕人畢業後到此一闖，加上娛樂設施豐富，有劇院也有大型演唱會場地，他強調伯明翰是「歐洲最年輕城市」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n料成另一個金融商業區<br />\n<br />\n以人口與GDP計，伯明翰已是全國第二大城市，又有國家展覽中心（NEC）設於機場旁，。。。。。。。。。。這大概是Tommy對伯明翰看得很牛的主因，「絕對準備醞釀中，只係俾疫情hold住咗。」<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【倫敦】侍應、售貨員有力置業<br />\n<br />\n雖然金融業難及香港、倫敦，但受HS2帶挈，。。。。。。。。。。、4,000個住宅單位、10,000個新職位。<br />\n<br />\n伯明翰曾是工業革命的重鎮，至今仍有不少工廠，如積架、上汽旗下MG等，還有亞馬遜的貨倉。。。。。。。。。。。。。。，不過Tommy盛讚香港人的效率，多番強調其工作方式可用諸全球：「香港人實在太醒目、太快手喇。」<br />\n<br />\n現時經營地產代理公司的Tommy認為，伯明翰租金低，地理優越，創業成本較香港輕，吸引許多中小企落腳，創業機會較香港多。<br />\n<br />\n在Tommy眼中，做生意與生活，。。。。。。。。。。。，他從家中步行五至十分鐘可抵公司、銀行，開車約兩小時亦可抵倫敦等城市。<br />\n<br />\n以Tommy生活經驗，治安宜憑富人、平民區估量，預算多的話可考慮市中心與SuttonColdfield、Solihull、Harborne、Edgbaston這四區，因區內。。。。。。。。。。。。。。。「最緊要做足功課。」是他對考慮移民者的寄語。"},{"pid":"bde6a428e731dcb26e96ca7d1e070e5d92e3829d","tid":2392712,"uid":191815,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:32:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>看得很牛的主因</strong>"},{"pid":"ccae1edcd7e3d7f7439cce4476950142cbec7486","tid":2392712,"uid":78295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bde6a428e731dcb26e96ca7d1e070e5d92e3829d","tid":2392712,"uid":191815,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:32:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>看得很牛的主因</strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:45:57.000Z","msg":"到底嘜鳩人寫呢篇野"},{"pid":"57400a39fe4f6903355219f055c48ee6fc215372","tid":2392712,"uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ccae1edcd7e3d7f7439cce4476950142cbec7486","tid":2392712,"uid":78295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bde6a428e731dcb26e96ca7d1e070e5d92e3829d","tid":2392712,"uid":191815,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:32:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>看得很牛的主因</strong>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:45:57.000Z","msg":"到底嘜鳩人寫呢篇野"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T03:51:00.000Z","msg":"都講咗, 蘋果係專請NDS畢業生<br />\n<br />\n佢地大中華到一個點, 係唔PREFER請本地香港人的<br />\n<br />\n講咗成年, 你地又唔信<br />\n<br />\n蘋果成日出蝗語, 一出, 你地又問點解<br />\n<br />\n講又唔信"},{"pid":"be43cfa77c38e319added59494ba8083c3518ba8","tid":2392712,"uid":364392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-03T07:14:15.000Z","msg":"睇完peaky blinders覺得呢個地方衰過九龍城寨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji